title: Multicolumn CSS Menu, Site Search - Swimbi(Mac 1.9.4)
description:
SWIMBI (Swift Menu Builder) - Mac App, feature-rich and so easy to use.

Multi-level drop down menus,
Icons - unlimited choice,
Multi-column menus,
Site search - built-in search field,
Totally configurable skings and configs,
Any colors, sizes, shadows, effects, animations, patterns and more,
unique CSS Menu with incredible ease.

Adavanced User Interface with Live Preview, drag-n-drop support.
  
http://swimbi.com/


One of the most annoying aspects of designing a website is the time you need to spend building the navigation menu.

This software will help you quickly build stylish CSS menus for your website without all trial and error we have all done in the past and the best part you do not need any coding knowledge to use this software.



               Features of Swimbi Swift Menu Builder

- Available for Mac, Windows and Chrome
- Easy download and install
- Easy to use user interface
- Live preview which gives you the ability to see changes as they happen.
- Hundreds of Icons already included in Swimbi with ability to get more icons using Icomoon app.
- Includes pre-built skins that you could use or use as a starting point and of course you could just start from scratch.
- Ability to design fixed menus, vertical menus, responsive menus and even fluid menus.
- Search on your website via Google
- Pattern overlays to give your menu that extra boost
- Multi level, multi column, unlimited drop down menus
- Mouse rollover styles which if you have some CSS3 or Java knowledge could be difficult to do on your own.
- Menu Shadows and Text Shadows
- And a Lot More
   
http://swimbi.com/download/
